 end="27.024">that&apos;s</span> <span begin="27.024" end="27.155">a</span> <span begin="27.199" end="27.393">co</span><span begin="27.432" end="27.518">p-</span><span begin="27.518" end="27.708">out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但你只敢匿名发发推特</span></p><p begin="27.778" end="32.130" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.778" end="27.930">And</span> <span begin="27.930" end="28.076">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="28.076" end="28.262">just</span> <span begin="28.291" end="28.602">like,</span> <span begin="28.602" end="29.274">&quot;Hey,</span> <span begin="30.731" end="30.871">are</span> <span begin="30.871" end="31.071">you</span> <span begin="31.115" end="31.356">o</span><span begin="31.411" end="32.130">kay?&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我只想说 嘿 你没事吧</span></p><p begin="34.095" end="36.194" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.095" end="34.225">And</span> <span begin="34.277" end="34.447">I</span> <span begin="34.447" end="34.593">ain&apos;t</span> <span begin="34.628" end="34.831">trying</span> <span begin="34.831" end="34.962">to</span> <span begin="34.992" end="35.138">mess</span> <span begin="35.138" end="35.273">with</span> <span begin="35.313" end="35.465">your</span> <span begin="35.465" end="35.721">self-</span><span begin="35.721" end="35.847">ex</span><span begin="35.847" end="36.019">pres</span><span begin="36.019" end="36.194">sion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我并不想干涉你的自我表达</span></p><p begin="36.219" end="37.226" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.219" end="36.371">But</span> <span begin="36.409" end="36.586">I&apos;ve</span> <span begin="36.586" end="36.765">learned</span> <span begin="36.765" end="36.926">the</span> <span begin="36.926" end="37.226">lesson</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而我吸取了教训</span></p><p begin="37.291" end="38.472" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.291" end="37.465">That</span> <span begin="37